company=E2=80=99s Bitcoins are now worth $36.6 billion, a $14.7 billion <i>=
gain</i>. <br/><br/>Microstrategy=E2=80=99s stock, up 683 percent in the la=
st year, has long been a great way to play the Bitcoin speculation game wit=
hout actually having to own any tokens. The company now has a market value =
