s a massive leveraged bet that will pay off bigly
if Bitcoin continues to increase in value, but very badly for investors if =
the price goes down.   <br/><br/>Saylor responded by spinning up a word sal=
ad so amazing that I=E2=80=99m not smart enough to decipher it. =E2=80=9CA =
