=99s spinning at 100 vol. So the way we make money is we=E2=80=99re selling=
 the volatility and recycling it back into Bitcoin, and we=E2=80=99re also =
stripping the volatility, the risk, and the performance off of fixed-income=
 securities, and we=E2=80=99re transferring that to the common stock. Our c=
ommon stock is delivering 2x Bitcoin, 2x vol. If you want to understand the=
 economics of this, we generate a spread. The BTC spread we generate is a f=
unction of the equity premium, the convert premium, and the Bitcoin premium=
=2E Bitcoin premium is the AR Bitcoi=
n versus the US dollar.=E2=80=9D<br/><br/=
